{"tid":1420032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到文宣見倒] 文宣方向整合！","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T09:00:59.000Z","uid":137849,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b982a9e2b8f3da9cec6b72c4d2ab6fe9c1803243","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:27:10.000Z","msg":"見倒好多唔同文宣嘅方向，好多idea都好值得發展。小弟不才，小小整合左啲。<br />\n<br />\n       1.<span style=\"font-size: large;\">   <span style=\"color: red;\">罷工</span></span><br />\n          今次三罷其實幾成功，尤其是<span style=\"color: red;\">機場罷工</span>。要大力宣傳今次三罷嘅影響力，感謝一切罷工人士嘅付出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n         目的係比和理非一個心理準備，<span style=\"color: red;\">三罷唔會淨係得一次</span>，預備長期抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t2.\t<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">荃灣+何妖</span></span><br />\n            仆你個街，講起就嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n            又係何妖嘅人斬鳩我地手足，又係<span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作</span>上次何妖咁撚樣都冇事，今次點都唔可以放過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n            仲有啲冚家產黑幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n            <span style=\"color: red;\">黑警交更</span>拉手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n           <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煲撚大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n\t3.\t<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各區催淚支援</span></span><br />\n            呢位巴打幾有想法，我幾認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【民意反擊戰】我地要做一樣黑警永遠做唔到嘅事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417880</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n         要落區對抗蛇齋餅糭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n\t4.  <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民間記者</span></span>會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【戰後檢討】我宣布反送中民間記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1419071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1419071</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n要有個公眾平台俾所有人了解我地嘅諗法，對抗港共節目&lt;四點鐘許蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n       5.<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">煽情post</span></span><br />\n        咩救個阿伯<br />\n        咩向公眾道歉<br />\n        總之要放我地嘅催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n       拉住民意，唔理有冇流失都好，我地都要俾人睇到呢一面。香港人最可愛嘅一面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n      <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t6.\t<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重申五大訴求</span></span><br />\n<br />\n          重申送中條例嘅恐怖...中共<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中營</span></span>...<br />\n          <br />\n         要開民智，自由係一切嘅基礎，咩安定繁榮穩定全部都不及<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自由</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n        有位巴打打左篇野，幾清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再post: 文宣攻勢開始啦，打左啲野大家幫手spread啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417298</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n\t7.\t<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">北角+何妖</span></span><br />\n            又係何妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n            咩福建幫福建佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有機會炒車，俾港共陰左去北角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同佢地結咗仇<br />\n            但打義士仲想洗白？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n            屌你老母拎住棍等人打都唔係咩好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n            文宣可以link多啲佢地去何妖(聽講有親<br />\n            Focus 多啲去啲<span style=\"color: red;\">狗放佢地上枱打義士</span><br />\n            仲有<span style=\"color: red;\">高空擲物</span>，跌落黎死人嫁屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n            點講都好北角真係紅到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下次遊行經過要小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 住北角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n\t8.\t<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">機場和你飛集會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n        最安全，最有效嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n        一定要<br />\n        唔多講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n\t9.  <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">葉虎事件</span></span><br />\n        <br />\n<br />\n        <span style=\"color: red;\">呢個係連結中共同鄉黑嘅證據</span><br />\n<br />\n\t10.\t<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">fb藍絲攻勢都唔好放鬆</span></span><br />\n          藍絲冇腦，睇得多就會信，唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n       11.   <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">攬炒巴</span></span><br />\n            要多啲支持佢，外國文宣好重要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n       12.  <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">統計手足損失，支援手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n          義士唔係condom，黑警做過嘅一切，要記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經有6位手足永遠離開咗我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔可以忘記，亦都唔敢忘記。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港共對我地做嘅一切，我一定唔會忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n     好多手足被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地一定要記得，等待來日清算警犬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足千萬要小心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n     個人而言，我最唔想手足受傷，有事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇要加？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家幫手諗下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"20c26b93b2e7dc7d87948b7f9599ddcb5ec94fb6","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:27:46.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d8b2dbdf2c469c72db736fa8489b7b99cc7fba","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:29:25.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"bd43ad179944a67c3a8873785ef026e2c6bdfe54","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:29:35.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"56cd7c810fb3a927b5398e925d9e6279f51d8f66","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:29:48.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"57b2321b2f16d196395debae6de9cdf8fdcf3785","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:30:01.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"818b6930c4fa961aedfd59ebce01392a72285a5c","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"b15b571393fc27b09a927ca92c3ccd8da2ff615d","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:30:24.000Z","msg":"代"},{"pid":"39c60de03456ec7a65f1f137072acd89f1dc14d2","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"革"},{"pid":"ceef381d5b789f05d2b8e66009731da59dde61a5","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:30:46.000Z","msg":"命"},{"pid":"429d3e13057c9d0462efbec7f0195d291b6071c8","tid":1420032,"uid":188810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:30:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6dd23406a444d9e2d8cd111c16c82688eeed567b","tid":1420032,"uid":93622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:31:08.000Z","msg":"幫你推！我今晚放工就搞圖！"},{"pid":"c399829510ecf2df62e35ca39d0834037c2ba23b","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1c01d9bc4286a7896ebc8051d9a78f3c3e4b5f3","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd23406a444d9e2d8cd111c16c82688eeed567b","tid":1420032,"uid":93622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:31:08.000Z","msg":"幫你推！我今晚放工就搞圖！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />辛苦巴打"},{"pid":"81d7844fdd71cc76d39611431727f6503fec28b8","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:32:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a926fcf58ac1e76c45db109604dac30c44f69bc","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:33:34.000Z","msg":"仲有冇其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80c6ec645eb70cd9c62dfa117bc2e6fecc7cbc3","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"再自舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a1c889057df5216940cee63e4a9ec339b9f469","tid":1420032,"uid":278583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"推 讚同而家到文宣朋友做野<br />\n<br />\n而家開始係打民意戰<br />\n<br />\n簡單講都係想做到2個效果<br />\n1）香港人被政府同警犬傷害，好慘。等全球都覺得香港可憐，係唔同層面對政府展壓）<br />\n<br />\n2）突顯政府政權有幾賤，務求要分化藍絲人士，拉攏更多淺藍支持。<br />\n<br />\n民意唔可以比佢地逆轉，如果唔係成個運動係歷史上會被黑化🤦&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"1139b062de8d9448f84dfd4d188b909522629538","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"順手share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n11點直播首場民間記者會 <a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/live331a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flive331a&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnA%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=54818652\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flive331a&h=15c917c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/live331a</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1419884\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1419884</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"084503e29aff95e5673f8ba66fe24541db1630e8","tid":1420032,"uid":138144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kLgZ3VS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkLgZ3VS.gif&h=47405cc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32947ee563e14c754b7ee47809bd67f3ecb2966e","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04a1c889057df5216940cee63e4a9ec339b9f469","tid":1420032,"uid":278583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"推 讚同而家到文宣朋友做野<br />\n<br />\n而家開始係打民意戰<br />\n<br />\n簡單講都係想做到2個效果<br />\n1）香港人被政府同警犬傷害，好慘。等全球都覺得香港可憐，係唔同層面對政府展壓）<br />\n<br />\n2）突顯政府政權有幾賤，務求要分化藍絲人士，拉攏更多淺藍支持。<br />\n<br />\n民意唔可以比佢地逆轉，如果唔係成個運動係歷史上會被黑化🤦&zwj;♂️"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:38:48.000Z","msg":"啱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實香港人真係好慘 更慘係咁都仲有藍絲撐警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc299e53c2d4e4f68145be19b4021d5d678296c","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0k0On8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0k0On8.png&h=cb90f5fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"543cdc64d5359872c0dff7086c680b9999dcdd5d","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:42:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不受傷、不被捕、不篤灰、不割席</span></span>"},{"pid":"91f52c0011eca90602d2f10cacc597cad660ee2f","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:43:47.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3457e3d25b8b6173e9b5fac4618c11c8e3a3116c","tid":1420032,"uid":137849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"再推！"}]}